reviews.review_text:
I GOT NO CHANCE OF LOSING..THIS TIME.. Easily the best show I ever attended.

SCATTERED BY THE WIND
Dreaming of changing seasons
Of leaves on an Autumn Morning
Being Scattered by the Wind

Some wait for years
in a river oftears
for a hero to save the day
but maybe even the clouds of confusion
will be Scattered by the Wind

Times moving faster than hands on a watch
got to be more to life
that clocks on a wall
All things so important
Now Scattered by the Wind

Modern Society 
Worships High Technology
Losing touch with Nature's reality
What will they do
When it is all Scattered by the Wind?

Deep in Enchanted Forests
Dancin bone to bone
Like Birds in Puddles play
Not afraid to be  Scattered by the Wind.

-ChrisFreedom
